Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了有限的生命，为了活着的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.20,0:03:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动乱的时代来到了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见·银河铁道999\N{\fs12}—安卓梅达终点站—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.62,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片源：乡乡樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译：ling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.12,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校译：yjh ling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间轴：xiaoD soma
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.60,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走不动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去就哪怕只剩一口气也要继续走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去就直到最后一口气也要继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去力气就会丢掉性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,999？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指银河铁道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西很久以前就已经停驶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河铁道也死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个时候真是令人怀念呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那曾是梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻时的事过后回想时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都像是梦想一样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐，痛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只剩下回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械化母星已经从宇宙消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想成为敌人阻击的靶子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他有点承受不了的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怪他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这一步\N谁都会感觉自己像是被逼到死胡同的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，喝吧 铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确看到普罗梅休姆死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看着机械化母星在粉碎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配这个世界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是永远的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统治这个世界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有拥有永远生命的机械身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有限的生命无非是空虚的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.10,0:10:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将筑起未来辉煌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被永远的生命支撑的永远的机械化世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯，有什么人往这边来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.10,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别..别开枪，是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来了传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有人叫 星野铁郎 吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...就是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是带给我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你坚持住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持，坚持住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过999号来没来可说不准哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大都会和中央车站都在机械人手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也要去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.60,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管希望多么小，也敢赌上自己的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，我们的小伙子说要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让他走好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下，跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停，快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的废墟，999号会来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子，别死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我挡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死在这种地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回头，快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.40,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99号月台...是搭乘999的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子999号恐怕不会在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您多时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就发车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您赶快上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机关车C62-48
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:18:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加压完毕，全系统没有异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发 前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快，赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快，铁郎先生，这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快，赶..赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分差点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，什么时候你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回地球的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崛起大地的泥土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会看到有我们的鲜血流出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.10,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看到那鲜血之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.30,0:23:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定回来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.60,0:23:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能平安无事真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.60,0:23:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很想念您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外您拿着车票吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.80,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公职在身，没有车票的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.80,0:24:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都不允许乘车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.10,0:24:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车长先生，之前梅蒂尔在哪里下的车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.40,0:24:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.90,0:24:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.60,0:24:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是冥王星吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是在我不知道的时候下了车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.10,0:24:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里下的嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.70,0:24:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的旅行也是不错的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.00,0:24:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械化人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.80,0:24:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.30,0:24:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是服务员，叫美达鲁麦娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.70,0:24:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美达鲁麦娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.70,0:24:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是库莱亚的后任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.00,0:24:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.80,0:25:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人，如果您要去餐车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.00,0:25:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身脏衣服可会让我们感到为难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.10,0:25:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许让您不高兴了，请包涵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.80,0:25:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的时代又是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.40,0:25:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样一个目的地不明的列车上做服务员的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.50,0:25:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也真是少见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.70,0:25:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地不明？这辆列车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.30,0:25:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不管怎么说目的地只有机关车自己知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.80,0:25:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这么不负责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.80,0:25:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在万分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.50,0:25:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的银河铁道成了什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.00,0:25:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连作为职员的我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.50,0:26:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.30,0:26:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样都要洗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.00,0:26:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.00,0:26:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.50,0:26:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服我会为您洗好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.30,0:26:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王星吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.80,0:26:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直认为梅蒂尔是在这里下的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.50,0:26:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.50,0:27:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.50,0:27:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.60,0:27:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.60,0:27:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.80,0:27:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.60,0:27:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.60,0:27:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.90,0:27:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真是不方便的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.90,0:27:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要吃这种不卫生的东西才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.90,0:27:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一点上，我们机械化人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.40,0:27:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用这种胶囊补充能量就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.30,0:27:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你这样的机械人来说，连吃的乐趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.10,0:27:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.40,0:28:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个奇怪的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.40,0:28:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做999号的服务员的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.70,0:28:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想得到这个世上最美的东西什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.20,0:28:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世上最美的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.50,0:28:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的...不过我可是一点也不懂她的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.70,0:28:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次什么事都不明白，我实在是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.60,0:28:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我去洗个澡轻松一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.60,0:28:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车长，车长先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.40,0:28:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.50,0:28:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号变成黄色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.70,0:29:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～现在不可以打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.20,0:29:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，有什么关系，不都是男人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.80,0:29:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我会感到为难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.40,0:29:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我会马上就去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.50,0:29:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使说不许开门，我也要想尽办法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.10,0:29:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.80,0:29:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.00,0:29:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.50,0:29:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这个声音是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向999号通告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.60,0:29:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入支线，让出主线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.50,0:29:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许挡住我的前进路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.60,0:29:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我行走在正式的轨道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.80,0:29:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让出轨道，愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.00,0:29:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幽灵列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.90,0:30:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵列车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.60,0:30:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个列车运的是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.30,0:30:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.20,0:30:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天为止，我从未被别的列车超越过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.20,0:30:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被这种不明底细的列车超过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.50,0:31:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心，这是999号的耻辱\N真是可耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.40,0:31:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叛乱的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.40,0:31:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.20,0:31:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.70,0:31:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托莱达分歧点所在的海彼美鲁达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.70,0:31:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其叛乱频繁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.80,0:31:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过被破坏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.10,0:31:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是机械化人的装甲列车和战车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.00,0:31:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛，宇宙里也有战友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.80,0:31:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，对了，我差点忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.00,0:31:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道下一站的站名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.90,0:31:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站 海彼美鲁达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.90,0:31:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海彼美鲁达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海彼美鲁达？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.00,0:31:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然预定中是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.30,0:31:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经的大弗隆迪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.80,0:31:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也因战乱导致大气有毒化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.60,0:31:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站的设施也被破坏，所以决定通过，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.20,0:31:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.50,0:32:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会临时在拉美塔尔停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.60,0:32:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉美塔尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.70,0:32:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海彼美鲁达的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.30,0:32:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以一千年为周期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.00,0:32:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行椭圆形轨道地公转，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.60,0:33:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉美塔尔 拉美塔尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.60,0:33:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本站下车的乘客请出示身份证明书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.90,0:33:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并接受所持物品的检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.50,0:33:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复通告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.10,0:33:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车的乘客请出示身份证明书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.30,0:33:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并接受所持物品的检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.60,0:33:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，这个星球也落入了机械化人的手里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.80,0:33:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是梅蒂尔小姐的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.60,0:33:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:36.10,0:33:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这里是梅蒂尔小姐的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.40,0:33:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信的话就请您自己亲眼去确认吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.10,0:33:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从这里出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.90,0:33:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.20,0:33:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是不要出去为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.90,0:34:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒得太严了，恐怕会被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.60,0:34:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.60,0:36:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟去哪里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.40,0:36:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能知道梅蒂尔的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.60,0:37:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.90,0:37:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.60,0:37:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你帮我包扎的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.50,0:37:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.30,0:37:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，我叫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.60,0:37:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星野铁郎，银河铁道的乘客是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.80,0:37:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保险，我查看了你的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.90,0:37:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是安德拉都星的妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.90,0:38:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不合地球人的口味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.00,0:38:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.60,0:38:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.20,0:38:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于非常艰苦的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.20,0:38:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们濒临绝境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.40,0:38:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们不能停止战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.80,0:38:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.10,0:38:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.70,0:38:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是流淌着鲜血的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.80,0:38:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一线的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.90,0:38:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有丝毫的可能性，人就要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.60,0:38:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始就在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.00,0:38:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家举起杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.20,0:38:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们为了人类的未来歌唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.90,0:39:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经多少次几乎放弃过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.00,0:39:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，每次都在心里这样回答自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.90,0:39:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有许多的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.70,0:39:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们中甚至有破坏了机械化母星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.20,0:40:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那不是结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.20,0:40:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明以为那就是结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.70,0:40:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.30,0:40:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星野铁郎这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.70,0:40:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说好像在哪里听说过呢，就是你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.00,0:40:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我凑巧救了为了不起的人物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.50,0:40:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.50,0:40:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火，开火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.50,0:40:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.60,0:40:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.50,0:40:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械化人在黑暗中也能看得见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:58.90,0:41:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要呆在原地，敌人就会行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.50,0:41:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自己会过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.40,0:41:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.40,0:42:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.60,0:42:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:28.50,0:42:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.30,0:42:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.80,0:42:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.50,0:42:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老爸的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.50,0:42:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和妈妈都被机械人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.80,0:42:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在安德拉都的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.90,0:42:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，你的家人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.00,0:42:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.00,0:43:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈被机械人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.30,0:43:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.00,0:43:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听妈妈说是死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.70,0:43:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与机械人战死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.10,0:43:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.30,0:43:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.20,0:43:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么在这个星球下车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.60,0:43:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.30,0:43:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.80,0:43:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位叫梅蒂尔的女性，没听说过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.40,0:43:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.90,0:43:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆女儿的梅蒂尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.00,0:43:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干的话，我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.30,0:43:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.50,0:43:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.00,0:43:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在被叫做普罗梅休姆的就是梅蒂尔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.20,0:43:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么，不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.50,0:43:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说梅蒂尔成了普罗梅休姆的接班人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.00,0:43:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.20,0:43:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.20,0:43:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔现在就是普罗梅休姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.20,0:43:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:55.90,0:43:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.40,0:44:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，铁郎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.50,0:44:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟普罗梅休姆长得一摸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.70,0:44:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.90,0:44:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个城堡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.30,0:44:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.80,0:44:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,999号的发车时间到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:55.40,0:44:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.10,0:44:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.30,0:45:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.10,0:45:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话，没办法突围出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.70,0:45:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈洛克舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:27.00,0:46:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就用那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.30,0:47:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见吧，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.80,0:47:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.70,0:47:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死在我前面哦，这可是男人间的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:17.60,0:47:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.80,0:47:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳头，很痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.80,0:47:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别死啊，妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:44.40,0:47:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.90,0:47:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底没有见到梅蒂尔小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.00,0:48:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.40,0:49:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.50,0:50:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.20,0:50:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.30,0:50:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎 请乘上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:43.10,0:50:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:45.10,0:50:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你喜欢的地方下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.10,0:50:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你愿意的地方，就拜托机关车开到那个行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.00,0:50:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么，不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.70,0:50:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说梅蒂尔成了普罗梅休姆的接班人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:57.30,0:50:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.20,0:51:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:29.40,0:51:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.90,0:51:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.90,0:51:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,999号以及其乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.70,0:51:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是支配银河铁道的黑骑士法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.30,0:51:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即前往控制中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.80,0:51:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关车先生，怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:56.90,0:51:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接受他的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.80,0:52:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻表将发生混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:00.80,0:52:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在支配银河铁道的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.00,0:52:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是银河铁道管理局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.40,0:52:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不听从我的命令，999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.70,0:52:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好破坏掉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:16.60,0:52:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机关车 C62-48
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:20.90,0:52:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能违背自己的良心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.00,0:52:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关车，请听从他的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:29.50,0:52:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:31.10,0:52:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.90,0:53:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘务员没有必要下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:27.20,0:53:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我有义务保护乘客的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:30.20,0:53:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:31.90,0:53:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:34.10,0:53:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据指示向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:57.80,0:53:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.20,0:54:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗梅休姆女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.70,0:54:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正伟大的宇宙的支配者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:04.90,0:54:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字永远不灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.20,0:54:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑，普罗梅休姆的确死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:09.40,0:54:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧，梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.50,0:54:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是黑骑士法斯特吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.70,0:54:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.10,0:54:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，为什么盯着我看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.30,0:55:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别盯着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:07.70,0:55:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:13.40,0:55:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:14.50,0:55:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把铁郎怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:17.20,0:55:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:18.80,0:55:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是让他在时间的彼端旅行一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:53.60,0:55:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:58.50,0:56:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:10.90,0:56:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:14.10,0:56:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:16.70,0:56:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.70,0:56:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈...妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.70,0:56:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.90,0:56:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.10,0:56:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样，我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.90,0:57:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈被杀害前一天的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:24.70,0:57:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊，一点都不暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:29.00,0:57:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里来，妈妈让你暖和起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:34.30,0:57:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖啊，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.10,0:57:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:40.50,0:57:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和妈妈呆在一起的最后的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:43.70,0:57:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候妈妈还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:47.70,0:57:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用温暖的手抱着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:51.00,0:57:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，明天终于可以到大都会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:54.90,0:57:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拼命帮妈妈干活买车票的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.60,0:58:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起乘上999号吧，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:01.70,0:58:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:08.10,0:58:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，趁现在告诉妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:11.20,0:58:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就不会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:13.60,0:58:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以改变时间的流向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.50,0:58:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，是我，是铁郎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:25.00,0:58:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，打开窗户啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:29.10,0:58:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.70,0:58:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像起风了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.20,0:58:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，把窗户打开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.90,0:58:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:41.10,0:58:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:44.60,0:58:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，开窗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:53.80,0:58:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下，不许杀我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.40,0:59:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:11.40,0:59:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，别杀了我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:15.10,0:59:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别杀了我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.50,0:59:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈...妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:41.20,0:59:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:47.40,0:59:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.90,0:59:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回顾过去的感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:52.00,0:59:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...是个悲剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:56.10,0:59:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法言语的悲剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:59.10,1:00:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉身的人死去的话，就一切都结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.10,1:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样仍想反抗普罗梅休姆女王吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:07.40,1:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想和我们一样永远活下去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.90,1:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有永远的生命...\N不对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.20,1:00:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡不是结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:16.20,1:00:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体里流淌着鲜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.00,1:00:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和被杀害的妈妈，大伯一样，流淌着鲜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:22.60,1:00:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对大伯发过誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.60,1:00:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定活着回到那个鲜血浸透的大地上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.60,1:00:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你向父亲发了誓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.60,1:00:31.30,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs12}（这两句话里的大伯和父亲在日语里是同一个词）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.30,1:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死去的大伯和伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:34.10,1:00:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为了我流了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.90,1:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛，那就是你的父亲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.40,1:00:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些叔叔们，我也要..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.20,1:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是战士的枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.20,1:00:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拔枪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.20,1:00:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都要跟我战斗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:55.00,1:00:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，拔枪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.50,1:01:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:02.70,1:01:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:20.00,1:01:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.10,1:01:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在原地敌人就会行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.10,1:01:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人会自己接近过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:58.80,1:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.00,1:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你学到的东西比我所预料的要多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:08.00,1:02:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在这里败给我，说不定对你是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.60,1:02:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:16.80,1:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信着有限生命的可贵而在旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.20,1:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这是向着绝望在旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.40,1:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快，这种会让你后悔的绝望的时刻就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:33.10,1:02:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说知道我和999号的目的地吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.50,1:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关车和梅蒂尔都知道你的目的地是何地
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.30,1:02:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔也知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.00,1:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.20,1:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着的话，以后再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:25.30,1:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔回来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.70,1:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没，还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.80,1:03:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:32.20,1:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.20,1:03:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开，放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.60,1:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.00,1:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾美拉达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.60,1:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,999 请停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.30,1:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.40,1:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就跌入宇宙的深渊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:24.30,1:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:26.00,1:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一直在继续着艰难的旅途啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:39.10,1:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，保卫梅蒂尔是你的义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:43.80,1:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果称得上男子汉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:00.80,1:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:02.90,1:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种美丽的容貌，美丽的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:07.20,1:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于可以得到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:16.10,1:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:26.60,1:06:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把梅蒂尔送到这里了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:28.50,1:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我想在这里好好看护梅蒂尔小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:44.50,1:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，我不会放弃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:47.90,1:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天，总有一天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.80,1:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站 摩在克行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:01.10,1:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车时间是2小时16分30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.20,1:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩在克行星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:07.20,1:07:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安卓梅达星云入口处的小行星，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:14.30,1:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安卓梅达啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.30,1:07:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这么远的地方了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:29.20,1:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，这次999停靠的摩再克行星是最后的机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:36.30,1:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了那里，就再也无法回头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:39.90,1:07:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.10,1:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一起在摩再克下车也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.30,1:07:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望的话\N就是在什么星球上一起度过一生也行，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:59.40,1:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？既然用传言卡叫我乘999
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:04.50,1:08:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却又说要我下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:07.20,1:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对继承了普罗梅休姆地位的流言
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:09.90,1:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不表示否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:12.00,1:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又用自己的身体来阻止我和法斯特的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:20.50,1:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的旅行中，净是我不明白的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:51.00,1:08:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不下车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:54.00,1:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.80,1:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:59.10,1:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.10,1:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会遇到什么情况都不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:03.40,1:09:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我也会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:04.70,1:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在这里逃避的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.40,1:09:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对不起死去的伙伴们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:09.80,1:09:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉也不要紧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:11.50,1:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.70,1:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回地球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:15.10,1:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回不去的，绝对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.00,1:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.90,1:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎是年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.10,1:09:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人不会去考虑失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:31.40,1:09:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇到几次挫折
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:33.50,1:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会相信最后会胜利，这才是真正的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:38.70,1:09:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有许多这样的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.30,1:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔小姐，您好像知道许多年轻人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.40,1:09:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我是旅行在时间长河中的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:51.30,1:09:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和数不清的众多年轻人一起旅行至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:59.50,1:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起感受快乐，一起体味痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:02.30,1:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后经验着死亡与分别至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:07.50,1:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会忘记一起旅行过的年轻人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:13.40,1:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个人的记忆都将深深刻在我的心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:19.00,1:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.50,1:10:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:07.60,1:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔，是你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.40,1:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.10,1:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:31.10,1:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔，是我，是星野铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.60,1:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.90,1:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.80,1:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是再也无法回头的旅途了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.90,1:12:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，你的目的地\N是安卓梅达星云中心的大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.10,1:12:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大安卓梅达行星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.50,1:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.00,1:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是大恒星云的重力平衡中心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:47.10,1:12:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配全宇宙的机械帝国的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.70,1:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我瞒着不说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:52.80,1:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的话，你一定会说要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:57.40,1:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不可能再活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.10,1:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么给我那个传音卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:02.90,1:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我给出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:04.70,1:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是诱使你前往大安卓梅达行星的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:11.70,1:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:13.38,1:13:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其这么麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:15.66,1:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始把我杀掉不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.38,1:13:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:21.14,1:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.38,1:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车长先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.94,1:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.30,1:13:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心事重重的样子，怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.34,1:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.46,1:13:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,999号无法走直线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.94,1:13:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法直线行驶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:32.98,1:13:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在虽然可以修正方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:36.22,1:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么力量在影响999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.02,1:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.54,1:13:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但右边的确有什么东西在强力地牵引着999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:46.14,1:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.14,1:13:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:02.86,1:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒后进入大安卓梅达行星重力圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:07.34,1:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力刹车最大出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:09.78,1:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30分45秒后到站
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:32.18,1:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终点站 大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:37.54,1:18:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.66,1:18:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往上层空间出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:43.66,1:18:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请至808电梯通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:48.70,1:18:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往地下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:50.18,1:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请至989下降电梯通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:55.38,1:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安卓梅达，安卓梅达，大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:02.06,1:19:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终点站 大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:07.26,1:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，你终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:10.34,1:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:15.78,1:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是来到这里的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:17.98,1:19:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有跟你战斗的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.34,1:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:22.86,1:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有携带武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:28.14,1:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔大人，迎接的人已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:31.78,1:19:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:33.82,1:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，你们先去上面的旅馆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:38.90,1:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:39.90,1:19:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我说的做，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:04.10,1:20:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看吧，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:06.58,1:20:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有死亡的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:09.30,1:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用担心饥饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:11.34,1:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是乌托邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:13.98,1:20:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人可以永远拥有无限的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:18.38,1:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你们人类而言短暂的青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:22.46,1:20:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里可以永远持续
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:29.94,1:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:30.98,1:20:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:34.18,1:20:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吃和美达鲁麦娜一样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:40.42,1:20:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种胶囊在这里制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:42.66,1:20:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向全宇宙提供
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.18,1:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是支撑着机械化世界的源泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:46.02,1:22:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:47.34,1:22:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿 梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:50.30,1:22:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:51.26,1:22:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还认我做母亲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.30,1:23:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和铁郎一起，把你的分身梅蒂尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.78,1:23:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人身的我破坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.74,1:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们各自失去了自己的一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:30.10,1:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间应该已经不再有憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:34.26,1:23:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在来好好谈谈吧，梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:36.46,1:23:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:38.10,1:23:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被所有人背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.38,1:23:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人们的驱赶中离开了我们的故乡拉美塔尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:48.10,1:23:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅带着我的女儿，你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:52.30,1:23:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来到这个无比荒芜的星球后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:56.74,1:24:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我靠自己一人的力量开始建筑机械星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:03.26,1:24:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后创造出了这个没有死亡的恐惧\N永远的机械化世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.34,1:24:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这曾是多么艰苦的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:12.90,1:24:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我的辛苦终于迎来报偿的日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:18.66,1:24:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后的事交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:21.34,1:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将成为这个行星的核心，度过余生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.66,1:24:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.30,1:24:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊，梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:44.90,1:24:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁、铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:47.70,1:24:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:48.62,1:24:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下万岁，梅蒂尔陛下万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.26,1:25:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下万岁，梅蒂尔陛下万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:03.66,1:25:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:13.90,1:25:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下万岁，梅蒂尔陛下万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:26.06,1:25:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:28.50,1:25:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:29.98,1:25:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.34,1:25:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么一起旅行至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.66,1:25:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.38,1:26:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:07.46,1:26:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔小姐叫您
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.42,1:26:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔叫我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:37.58,1:26:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.74,1:26:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:40.10,1:26:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要牢牢记住在这里看到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:00.62,1:27:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么幽灵列车会在这个地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:07.78,1:27:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.26,1:27:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打开这里的只有女王陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.38,1:27:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:15.42,1:27:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了，女王陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:17.74,1:27:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵循您的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:19.34,1:27:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除门锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:34.66,1:27:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:35.58,1:27:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽取生命之火的工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.74,1:27:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:04.14,1:28:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么会...这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:20.10,1:29:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:24.22,1:29:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:58.26,1:30:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安德拉都星的妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:02.30,1:30:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别死在我前面哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:04.34,1:30:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是男人间的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.06,1:30:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妙塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:16.94,1:30:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不成样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:18.10,1:30:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了人死什么的就哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:22.46,1:30:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子为了朋友流泪不是可耻的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:31.46,1:30:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有为了你哭泣的朋友吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:50.42,1:30:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个，你还觉得这里是乐园吗，美达鲁麦娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:56.58,1:30:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧，你吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:59.78,1:31:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是生命之火，你不吃吗！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:07.26,1:31:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:12.94,1:31:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么永远的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:17.22,1:31:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠牺牲别人生命的地方叫什么乐园？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:23.82,1:31:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们全部被捕了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:28.74,1:31:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美达鲁麦娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:32.58,1:31:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美达鲁麦娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:44.94,1:31:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美达鲁麦娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:51.42,1:31:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想拥有永远的生命\N和宇宙中最美的梅蒂尔小姐的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:58.46,1:32:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却变成了这样，我失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:01.70,1:32:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:03.26,1:32:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美达鲁麦娜，你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:09.38,1:32:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意为了我哭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:21.38,1:32:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:20.46,1:33:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，赶快让那些人登上999号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:24.26,1:33:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之前要先做一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:26.42,1:33:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样也要把普罗梅休姆打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.10,1:33:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒我母亲的，不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:35.86,1:33:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:37.74,1:33:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的双手打倒她，是我的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:45.06,1:33:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底还是背叛了我，梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:48.34,1:33:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托付给你一切，只想宁静地沉睡的你的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:55.70,1:33:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:57.82,1:34:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.38,1:34:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:03.54,1:34:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把梅蒂尔杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.42,1:34:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎怎么处置？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:08.90,1:34:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎只是因为你的请求才招来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:13.14,1:34:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终归，他是机械化世界的宿敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:17.70,1:34:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他活着也没有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:22.42,1:34:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会说下不了手吧，法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:44.22,1:34:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在恭候您，梅蒂尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:49.66,1:34:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵照普罗梅休姆女王陛下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:52.02,1:34:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来取您的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.98,1:34:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.30,1:34:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:59.50,1:35:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，这家伙交给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:10.30,1:35:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，你在干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:12.54,1:35:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让你的母亲死掉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:15.78,1:35:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这个把你精心抚养成人的母亲死吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:20.78,1:35:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:26.14,1:35:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我，母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:45.26,1:35:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:47.30,1:35:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是梅蒂尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:50.30,1:35:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是支配全宇宙的机械帝国的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:53.06,1:35:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大安卓梅达行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:56.82,1:35:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我自身
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.62,1:36:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，我为了托付未来而养育的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.74,1:36:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然背叛于我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:05.78,1:36:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧，灭亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:07.86,1:36:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和这些人类一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:12.26,1:36:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:18.38,1:36:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗舰两艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:19.62,1:36:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在向绝对机械圈内侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:21.34,1:36:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:58.30,1:37:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个震动是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:44.38,1:37:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是发生了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:53.02,1:37:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生，梅蒂尔小姐，请赶快上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:01.78,1:38:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:04.30,1:38:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在磨蹭什么，赶快，梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:10.82,1:39:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是战斗卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:24.10,1:39:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃到前面的车厢去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:43.54,1:39:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈洛克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:59.86,1:40:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹道在向右弯曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:07.70,1:40:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，弹道在偏向右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:12.30,1:40:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:15.62,1:40:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:17.50,1:40:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右方有股异常强大的引力在发生着作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:20.50,1:40:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:32.22,1:40:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？受到损伤了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:33.58,1:40:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有股可怕的重力在发生作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:37.50,1:40:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:40.78,1:40:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:42.90,1:40:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:44.82,1:40:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女吟唱时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:47.26,1:40:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切生命之火都会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:51.86,1:40:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是安卓梅达自古以来的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:57.82,1:40:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:59.70,1:41:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那种东西会来这里，为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:32.14,1:41:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女，追求着异质的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:36.62,1:41:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙飘荡的大暗黑彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:42.10,1:41:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为普罗梅休姆让这里充满机械能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:47.18,1:41:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎连的魔女就是被这个吸引而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.34,1:41:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是机械帝国的机械能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:52.46,1:41:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招来了莎连的魔女吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:54.94,1:41:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，因为我现在也是机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:58.38,1:42:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会睡一小会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:01.98,1:42:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了，朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.18,1:42:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭自动操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:21.82,1:42:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转换为手动操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:24.54,1:42:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用机械能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:26.34,1:42:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用手动驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:58.86,1:42:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后喷气推进装置全开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:00.70,1:43:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向左方22度修正方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:14.86,1:43:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:33.70,1:43:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:38.10,1:43:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和铁郎最后对决的时刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:43.38,1:43:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意为我们见证吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:46.34,1:43:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:47.82,1:43:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能发誓不管哪一方赢都不会出手吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:52.42,1:43:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:53.62,1:43:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，这会成为痛苦的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:57.34,1:43:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在这场战斗里获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:59.54,1:44:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和铁郎都不会有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:08.54,1:44:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:21.66,1:44:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:26.58,1:44:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拥有人形的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:51.70,1:44:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，哈洛克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:56.30,1:44:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:07.70,1:45:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还称我为朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:21.82,1:45:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意替我保管吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:25.42,1:45:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:00.18,1:46:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就要见证这个世上最痛苦的事情了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:05.54,1:46:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈洛克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:20.50,1:47:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:21.50,1:47:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,功率提高到这种程度应该可以脱出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:24.62,1:47:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,999号上面好像还有机械能量在发生作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:42.66,1:47:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:06.22,1:48:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:11.70,1:48:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住，法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:16.06,1:48:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:17.22,1:48:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是法斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:18.46,1:48:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士乘上这辆列车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:21.38,1:48:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，这次无论谁都没有退路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:27.82,1:48:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想求饶的话就趁现在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:29.58,1:49:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:32.14,1:49:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是任何人都无法干涉的男人间的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:35.70,1:49:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果为了铁郎着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:37.70,1:49:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不要干涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:18.26,1:50:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有光，我也能看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:23.58,1:50:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次也是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.70,1:50:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:27.70,1:50:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就到你的身边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:31.70,1:50:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能耐得住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:41.22,1:51:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你变强壮了...铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:01.22,1:52:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:36.06,1:52:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见...儿子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:50.70,1:52:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，我的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:44.70,1:54:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷，好冷...好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:49.70,1:54:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，来温暖我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:55.38,1:55:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔，我可爱的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:00.70,1:55:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔...梅蒂尔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:24.54,1:55:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你妈妈和你乘坐过的宇宙飞船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:27.98,1:55:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲带着我到达的小小的岩石的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:32.50,1:55:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个星球上，一边和孤独抗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:34.70,1:55:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边创造出永远生命的世界的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:38.22,1:55:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信会好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:44.26,1:55:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是位了不起的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:08.34,1:56:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫长而艰苦的旅途啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:11.54,1:56:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个旅途也终于结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:20.82,1:56:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:17.38,1:57:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要回地球去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:21.54,1:57:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:22.18,1:57:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我与为了我死去的同伴们的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:25.78,1:57:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被救的所有人也说要一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:29.46,1:57:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:52.70,1:57:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:54.02,1:57:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲是，当年与我和艾美拉达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:57.22,1:58:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起并肩战斗的了不起的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:01.34,1:58:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然中途我们不幸选择了不同道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:04.42,1:58:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:05.70,1:58:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很像你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:11.10,1:58:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:12.94,1:58:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你和父亲的志向不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:15.78,1:58:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要越过这个难关，未来要由年轻人来创造
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:21.26,1:58:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜血由父母传向儿女，儿女再传向他们的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:25.82,1:58:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远地持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:29.50,1:58:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这才是真正的永远的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:39.10,1:58:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车长先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:40.46,1:58:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，欢迎您回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.34,1:58:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:43.66,1:58:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也终于想通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:45.62,1:58:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:48.98,1:58:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉体的身体好，还是机械的身体好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.74,1:58:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个迷惑不已的自己太丢脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:55.06,1:58:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我下定决心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:57.26,1:58:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选择哪一种？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:59.50,1:59:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:01.06,1:59:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是原来的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:06.46,1:59:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子的话洗澡也没用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:30.62,1:59:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:32.46,1:59:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能跟铁郎一起走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:36.34,1:59:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一样，在没有终结的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:40.02,1:59:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间长河中跋涉的旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:44.26,1:59:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:48.94,1:59:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先上车吧，铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:51.42,1:59:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:01.18,2:00:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的旅途没有尽头
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:46.94,2:00:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:05.70,2:01:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:32.58,2:01:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:36.18,2:01:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天，分别会到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:38.62,2:01:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心里早就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:41.46,2:01:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你青春的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:44.10,2:01:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有年轻人才能见到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:46.02,2:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在时间长河中旅行的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:50.38,2:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:52.42,2:01:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能留在铁郎的心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:55.54,2:01:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就够了...我这样就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:59.90,2:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:04.02,2:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的青春一起旅行过的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:08.26,2:02:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:11.74,2:02:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 我的铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:18.86,2:02:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:33.22,2:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:37.90,2:02:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:47.50,2:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时光流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:49.02,2:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔逐渐消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:51.54,2:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像少年的时光不会倒流一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:55.02,2:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅蒂尔也不再回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:59.38,2:04:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:01.14,2:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,999号是曾在铁郎内心中奔跑的叫做青春的列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:48.90,2:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在再一次 怀着万千的思绪 汽笛鸣响
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:54.82,2:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在再一次 怀着万千的思绪 列车奔驰
